==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: help [[w:King Zhou of Shang|(King) Zhou (of Shang)]] to perform his cruelty

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' zhù zhòu wéi nuè)
# to help the wicked perpetrate wicked deeds;  to help a tyrant to do evil

